### Customer Registration
POST http://localhost:4000/auth/register/customer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "john_customer",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "fullName": "John Doe",
  "phoneNumber": "+1234567890",
  "address": "123 Main St, City, State",
  "role": "CUSTOMER"
}

### Employee Registration (Admin access required)
POST http://localhost:4000/auth/register/employee
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "username": "jane_employee",
  "email": "jane@company.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "fullName": "Jane Smith",
  "phoneNumber": "+1234567891",
  "address": "456 Work St, City, State",
  "role": "EMPLOYEE"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:4000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "john_customer",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Check Email Availability
GET http://localhost:4000/auth/check-email/test@example.com

### Get User Profile
GET http://localhost:4000/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

### Logout
POST http://localhost:4000/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
